name: My-picture
overview:
My-picture is art printing company providing its services for UK customers. Now it’s possible to provide gallery style prints for personal needs as well. Personal photos or pictures can become as art for own house or apartment. To satisfy different type of needs company is offering several types of prints and sizes.

My-picture is offering three types of prints: -Canvas prints – image is printed on white artistic canvas and stretched on the wooden frame; -Aluminium prints – image is printed on aluminum panel and covered with transparent glossy film for shine and protection. This type of print is light and water resistant. -Acrylic prints – image is printed on acrylic glass. This type of print is light and water resistant.

There is no need for help from experts to make small changes in actual interior. Family portrait or landscape photo now can be printed and hung on the wall. Even photos from point and shoot cameras can be good enough for art prints. So provides services are not only for professionals.

Image for any of three type prints can be uploaded directly to the website. System is offering additional options for each print during a step-by-step purchase process. Free images are available for customers needs in a case if they don’t have their own pictures. Special effects for each image are available after choosing a size for desired print. Delivery for all prints is available in UK.
